[GASPING]

34:36.420 --> 34:37.500
Turn it off.

34:41.621 --> 34:44.429
See... Now you wide awake.

34:44.449 --> 34:46.489
You're the reason
I fucking started using again.

34:46.510 --> 34:48.500
Man, dry off and get dressed.

34:52.510 --> 34:54.389
See?

34:54.409 --> 34:56.409
That's how you shoot dope.

34:56.429 --> 34:57.490
It's a creme brulee torch.

34:57.510 --> 34:58.580
Is that a brand?

