35:07.430 --> 35:09.500
Hey. Please don't.

35:13.510 --> 35:15.480
[TOILET FLUSHING]

35:15.500 --> 35:18.420
- [MUSIC PLAYING]
- Full Windsor or half?

35:18.440 --> 35:19.570
What's the difference?

35:19.590 --> 35:20.580
I got it.

35:20.600 --> 35:22.450
I got to do my hair.

35:24.370 --> 35:25.450
Put on your suit.

35:28.600 --> 35:31.380
What are you, deaf? Get up.

35:31.400 --> 35:33.580
Yo, let's do this.
Couple hours, and you go home.

35:36.420 --> 35:37.570
I want to see my dog.

35:37.590 --> 35:39.470
We don't have time.

35:39.490 --> 35:42.390
You show me Pepper or I'm
not doing anything you say.

35:45.400 --> 35:47.500
Put on your fucking suit right now.

35:49.400 --> 35:52.590
Redirect. Control. Attack.

35:53.370 --> 35:54.500
