- [ED] Calm down.

36:16.410 --> 36:18.520
- [KISBYE] Help! Help!
- [DOOR RATTLING]

36:18.540 --> 36:20.470
- Help me! Somebody help me...
- [LOUIS] No, no, no, no, no!

36:20.490 --> 36:21.600
[KISBYE GROANS]

36:23.410 --> 36:24.580
- [ED] Damn it!
- [LOUIS] God damn it!

36:24.600 --> 36:26.430
