I had to shut him up.

36:26.450 --> 36:27.560
World-famous fucking celebrity...

36:27.580 --> 36:29.480
- He was freaking out.
- Stop talking.

36:29.500 --> 36:30.540
Check the hallway.

36:32.380 --> 36:33.590
Cameras.

36:34.370 --> 36:35.450
Just in the elevators.

36:35.470 --> 36:38.560
- You sure?
- No.

36:38.580 --> 36:41.510
That was two shots. Somebody
has got to have heard that.

36:42.470 --> 36:43.560
Hey. No one in the hall.

36:44.510 --> 36:47.370
Aw, man! My suit!

36:47.390 --> 36:49.400
This was a suicide.

36:50.450 --> 36:52.430
Slug in the leg?

36:52.450 --> 36:55.400
They'll think he had a gun, and
the first shot was a mistake.

36:56.450 --> 36:58.440
It's what fucking happened.

36:58.460 --> 36:59.560
Got a better idea?

37:01.520 --> 37:02.560
Give me the pistol.

37:04.440 --> 37:05.580
[ED] Wipe everything down.

37:08.570 --> 37:12.370
You can ask me
why I set my sink on fire.

37:13.470 --> 37:14.570
Thought hadn't crossed my mind.

37:16.317 --> 37:17.410
[WASHING MACHINE WHIRRING]

37:17.430 --> 37:18.540
My family has this house...

37:18.560 --> 37:23.540
Or, had... this house, and it's
fallen on me to clean it out.

37:23.560 --> 37:26.600
And I saw some photos...

37:28.490 --> 37:32.370
Saw some photos of some shit
that I'd rather not remember.

37:32.390 --> 37:35.590
I am the least fucked-up
person in my family,

37:36.370 --> 37:38.480
so I feel like I deserve
some credit for that.

37:40.550 --> 37:41.600
Credit given.

37:46.420 --> 37:47.480
What were you running from?

37:49.480 --> 37:51.450
I wasn't running.

37:51.470 --> 37:55.430
You didn't pack a bag. You got in
the car, just started driving?

37:55.450 --> 37:57.083
Sounds like denial to me.

37:59.430 --> 38:01.570
- I wasn't.
- Okay.

38:06.430 --> 38:09.450
When I first got to LA,
I knew what I wanted.

38:09.470 --> 38:10.684
I wanted to make a movie.

38:10.695 --> 38:13.500
I wanted to salvage what
was left of my marriage.

38:13.520 --> 38:15.450
And I wanted to get closer to my kid.

38:15.470 --> 38:16.580
And?

38:18.450 --> 38:19.520
Marriage is done.

38:22.380 --> 38:24.380
Kid... She's seeing a shrink,

38:24.400 --> 38:27.460
so she can tell someone
how fucked-up her dad is.

38:27.480 --> 38:29.440
- And the movie?
- The... [SIGHS]

38:30.540 --> 38:33.380
It's desperately mediocre.

38:33.400 --> 38:35.530
I'm skipping the premiere right now,

38:35.550 --> 38:37.510
which is on in about 45 minutes.

38:39.430 --> 38:40.490
So...

38:43.480 --> 38:44.510
So what now?

38:46.390 --> 38:47.470
I don't know.

38:51.420 --> 38:52.500
But what do you want?

38:56.570 --> 38:58.370
What do I want?

39:03.480 --> 39:05.470
[SIGHS]

39:05.490 --> 39:08.540
I get it. You want to wallow
around in everything that's bad.

39:08.560 --> 39:12.470
I'm not judging,
'cause I love doing that...

39:12.490 --> 39:15.440
but there is a thing
called chakra therapy...

39:15.460 --> 39:16.570
Oh, man.

39:16.590 --> 39:19.550
I knew it. I knew you were
gonna bring this shit up.

39:19.570 --> 39:24.500
People come from all over the country
to sit for my crystal ceremony,

39:24.520 --> 39:26.530
and it changes their lives.

39:28.430 --> 39:29.510
"Crystal ceremony"?

39:33.390 --> 39:34.440
[CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

39:35.470 --> 39:37.400
[MAID HUMMING]

39:45.500 --> 39:47.380
Housekeeping.

39:48.410 --> 39:49.440
[BEEPS]

39:54.590 --> 39:56.500
[EXCLAIMS IN SPANISH]

39:57.440 --> 39:58.590
[GASPING]

40:10.570 --> 40:13.370
Max? It's David.

40:14.580 --> 40:16.370
It's time to go, mate.

40:24.480 --> 40:25.560
Oh, my God.

40:27.400 --> 40:29.410
[EXCITED CHATTER]

40:31.400 --> 40:32.520
[CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING]

40:37.510 --> 40:39.530
- Come on.
- [CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

40:39.550 --> 40:41.490
Ah... You look...

40:41.510 --> 40:43.470
- I know.
- [CHUCKLES]

40:44.390 --> 40:45.370
Come on.

40:45.390 --> 40:46.440
[CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING]

40:56.590 --> 40:58.450
[RICK] Okay.

40:58.470 --> 41:00.580
We gotta get inside, guys. Thank you.

41:01.490 --> 41:03.460
Hey.

41:03.480 --> 41:05.570
That's a buyer. And his wife. Uh...

41:05.590 --> 41:08.520
What the hell is her name?
Oh, I don't know.

41:10.380 --> 41:11.580
Where's everyone?

41:11.600 --> 41:13.358
The limos were backed up at the hotel.

41:13.369 --> 41:15.440
I'm sure they're right behind us.

41:15.460 --> 41:17.390
[SIRENS WAILING]

41:20.550 --> 41:22.460
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

41:24.380 --> 41:26.540
[RICK] Oh, he's in that vampire movie.

41:26.560 --> 41:28.440
Yeah.

