- Huh?

41:34.460 --> 41:37.390
Obviously, we should
cancel the screening.

41:37.410 --> 41:39.520
What? What's going on?

41:39.540 --> 41:43.510
[SIGHS] Oh, Max was found in his room.

41:43.530 --> 41:46.570
They're saying suicide.

41:47.560 --> 41:48.590
Max Kisbye?

41:49.370 --> 41:51.430
[SIGHS] I'm sorry.

41:53.570 --> 41:54.600
Oh, Jesus.

41:55.380 --> 41:58.390
We done here? Let's see this movie.

42:01.520 --> 42:02.530
[SIGHS]

42:05.560 --> 42:10.390
Still haven't learned the
principles of fire safety, I see.

42:10.410 --> 42:12.390
Take off your shirt and lie down.

42:12.540 --> 42:14.460
Shirt off. Okay.

42:19.600 --> 42:21.470
[SIGHS HEAVILY]

