Repeat after me.

42:31.460 --> 42:32.510
I am awake.

42:33.460 --> 42:35.400
I am alive.

42:35.420 --> 42:36.580
I'm open to change.

42:38.420 --> 42:40.480
I am awake.

42:40.500 --> 42:42.540
- I am alive.
- Be serious.

42:42.560 --> 42:44.600
What was the last part? I...

42:46.480 --> 42:48.460
I am open to change.

42:52.600 --> 42:56.500
This is your root chakra, for stability.

42:56.520 --> 42:57.590
[MILES] Hmm.

43:02.380 --> 43:07.400
Fire agate, on the sacral
