43:07.420 --> 43:09.440
If you want to cop a feel,
you just have to ask.

43:09.460 --> 43:11.530
If you don't make an effort,
I can't help you.

43:11.550 --> 43:13.490
Mmm-hmm. Okay.

43:15.370 --> 43:18.450
This draws out negative energy.

43:21.380 --> 43:22.430
Huh.

43:26.470 --> 43:29.420
Rose quartz on your heart chakra,

43:30.510 --> 43:32.520
to help you outrun who you were.

43:43.390 --> 43:46.480
Turquoise, to find who you are now.

43:50.570 --> 43:52.420
[INHALES DEEPLY]

43:52.440 --> 43:54.400
Breathe with me.

43:54.420 --> 43:57.440
- In.
- [BOTH INHALE DEEPLY]

43:57.460 --> 44:01.580
- And out.
- [BOTH EXHALE DEEPLY]

44:01.600 --> 44:05.370
I'm getting so tired, I can
hardly keep my eyes open.

44:05.390 --> 44:06.510
The crystals are working.

44:07.560 --> 44:10.460
The last one, selenite.

44:11.500 --> 44:12.600
Liquid light.

44:13.380 --> 44:14.510
Very powerful.

44:16.550 --> 44:18.580
So you can see the path forward.

44:20.580 --> 44:24.500
Things you've lost are gone forever.

44:24.520 --> 44:28.520
Everything else, everything
that belongs to you,

44:28.540 --> 44:31.590
that's yours, right in front of you.

44:33.450 --> 44:35.470
All you have to do is claim it.

44:39.370 --> 44:41.370
[MILES EXHALING DEEPLY]

44:55.430 --> 44:56.560
[GLADYS] Yes, canceled.

44:56.580 --> 45:01.390
We can try to, um,
get you a screener but...

45:01.550 --> 45:03.530
Yeah, okay. Thanks.

45:04.490 --> 45:06.390
[SIGHS]

45:06.410 --> 45:09.390
- I'm so sorry.
- Crazy.

45:09.410 --> 45:11.370
Poor Max.

45:11.390 --> 45:12.540
And your first premiere.

45:14.460 --> 45:16.520
Not to mention our date.

45:16.540 --> 45:18.400
We'll make time in LA.

45:18.420 --> 45:20.285
[SIGHS] This week is gonna be tough.

45:23.380 --> 45:24.570
I'm really looking forward to it.

45:25.550 --> 45:26.580
I swear.

45:27.590 --> 45:29.490
You're so beautiful.

45:30.480 --> 45:31.600
Am I allowed to say that?

45:32.560 --> 45:34.430
You are.

45:34.450 --> 45:36.520
- [CHUCKLES]
- [CELL PHONE RINGING]

45:36.540 --> 45:39.400
- Um, I'm sorry. [CHUCKLES]
- Mmm-hmm.

45:39.420 --> 45:41.430
Hey, this is Gladys.

45:41.450 --> 45:43.410
