45:52.540 --> 45:54.370
Is she angry?

46:00.380 --> 46:01.430
[DOOR OPENS]

46:08.500 --> 46:09.570
Tia, I don't know what you heard...

46:09.590 --> 46:11.520
Do you love me?

46:12.580 --> 46:14.420
Of course, I love you.

46:15.480 --> 46:16.570
Why do you lie?

46:16.590 --> 46:20.500
- What...
- We had to sell this movie to pay back LA.

46:20.520 --> 46:22.540
