46:22.560 --> 46:24.490
[BREATHING SHAKILY]

46:26.400 --> 46:28.570
The guy went crazy on me, Tia.

46:28.590 --> 46:30.560
Grabbed my gun,
started screaming for help.

46:31.540 --> 46:32.580
