48:18.490 --> 48:19.550
[GRUNTS SOFTLY]

48:42.490 --> 48:44.776
- [BUTTONS CLICK]
- [LINE RINGING]

48:45.590 --> 48:49.380
Hi, Arvin. It's Miles from Room 18.

48:49.400 --> 48:51.600
Did Jinny check out this morning?

48:52.380 --> 48:54.390
Yes, I'm calling from her room.

48:54.410 --> 48:58.500
No, I just... I just wanna know,
do you know her last name?

48:58.520 --> 49:00.590
I understand that, but I'm
sure she wouldn't mind.

