50:13.430 --> 50:15.786
[PEPPER YIPPING]

50:18.570 --> 50:21.520
Yeah, yeah, yeah. Good girl.

50:22.544 --> 50:24.540
[DOORBELL RINGS]

50:29.470 --> 50:31.500
- Hi.
